рода – Ukrainian" lang="uk" hreflang="uk" class="interlanguage-link-target">Українська</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-vi"><a href="https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/L%C3%A3o_R%C3%A2u_Xanh" title="Lão Râu Xanh – Vietnamese" lang="vi" hreflang="vi" class="interlanguage-link-target">Tiếng Việt</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-zh"><a href="https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%97%8D%E9%AC%8D%E5%AD%90" title="藍鬍子 – Chinese" lang="zh" hreflang="zh" class="interlanguage-link-target">中文</a></li></ul>
